Package org.apache.logging.log4j.util

Annotation Type InternalApi

@Retention(CLASS) @Documented public @interface InternalApi
Indicates that the annotated element is considered an internal API to Log4j and should not be used by external code. Internal APIs do not provide any stability guarantees between versions.
Since:
2.22.0
